long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is an extension for students of University of Technology, Sydney (UTS). The UTS library provides a proxy for students to access some scholar resources, such as ACM Digital Library and IEEExplore, which are unable to be downloaded without using the proxy. Although we can manually change the URL, this extension open a new page to visit the current page via the UTS Library proxy by 1-Click.
